Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of multiple sensors for autonomous vehicles and mobile robotic systems, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also focuses on deep learning approaches for multimodal odometry estimation and localization, which involves computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a new fusion module for sensor data, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and control systems (cs.SY).
